URL = http://www.openingdesign.com/


=Description=

"OpeningDesign is an open, online community where building professionals can ask and answer all manner of building-related questions, whether it be a quick technical question, or quick critique of a design. A website where professionals can share content, from a simple BIM or CAD detail to complex spec document. And, if your looking for more than just asking and answering questions, OD.com is also a place where you can solicit and bid on small scopes of work.... whether that be a quick 3d rendering job or help drawing up a simple building elevation.

And finally, OpeningDesign is place where the online collaboration tools used to help the community run smoothly, can also be used privately, to help your firm’s projects a little more smoothly as well. In this way, we like to think of OpeningDesign as 51% community, and 49% online tools."



